OL,3,CStates of Guernsey rejects proposed
OL,4,Cincome tax rise but paves way for GST
OL,6,FGuernsey politicians have thrown out
OL,7,Fthe island's proposed 2% rise in
OL,8,Fincome tax as part of the 2025 Budget
OL,9,Fbut have paved the way for the
OL,10,Fintroduction of a Goods and Services
OL,11,FTax (GST) in 2027.
OL,13,FThe decision followed four days of
OL,14,FStates of Guernsey politicians
OL,15,Fdebating through 22 amendments for the
OL,16,FBudget to try and plug a #100 million
OL,17,Fshortfall.
