OL,3,CStates of Guernsey rejects proposed
OL,4,Cincome tax rise but paves way for GST
OL,6,FDeputies have since debated whether to
OL,7,Fintroduce the previously planned 2%
OL,8,Fincrease on income tax, or - for the
OL,9,Ffourth time this political term -
OL,10,Fdebate the introduction of a 5% goods
OL,11,Fand services tax to the island.
OL,13,FOne budget amendment, originally voted
OL,14,Fthrough by deputies, suggested a
OL,15,Fhybrid approach where income tax would
OL,16,Fhave risen by 2% for two years until
OL,17,F2027, at which point GST would replace
OL,18,Fit.
