OL,3,CStates of Guernsey rejects proposed
OL,4,Cincome tax rise but paves way for GST
OL,6,FIn the end, deputies voted tonight (8
OL,7,FNovember) not to increase income tax,
OL,8,Fcreating uncertainty over the future
OL,9,Fof Guernsey's long-term finances.
OL,11,FIn setting out his Budget proposals,
OL,12,Fthe President of Policy and Resources,
OL,13,FDeputy Lyndon Trott was clear that the
OL,14,Fproposed increase in income tax of two
OL,15,Fpence in the pound was not a long term
OL,16,Fsolution.
