OL,3,CStates of Guernsey rejects proposed
OL,4,Cincome tax rise but paves way for GST
OL,6,FHowever, he warned that without extra
OL,7,Frevenue, the next States will find
OL,8,Fitself firefighting resources which
OL,9,Fare under increasing pressure from the
OL,10,Fageing demographic.
OL,12,FHe explained: "The irony is that if
OL,13,FGST is considered the answer in
OL,14,Ffuture, it's very likely that the
OL,15,Fintroduction rate will be much higher
OL,16,Fthan it's currently proposed because
OL,17,Fof the requirement to play catch up
OL,18,Fwith the damage that we've done to
OL,19,Fpublic finances."
